# SMS Configuration Examples
# Choose ONE of the following SMS services:

# ===== TWILIO (Global, Recommended for testing) =====
TWILIO_SID=ACxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+1234567890

# ===== UNIFONIC (Saudi Arabia) =====
UNIFONIC_APP_SID=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
UNIFONIC_SENDER_ID="Digital Edge"

# ===== TAQNYAT (Saudi Arabia) =====
TAQNYAT_API_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
TAQNYAT_SENDER="Digital Edge"

# ===== AWS SNS (Use existing AWS credentials) =====
# AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your_key
# AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your_secret
# AWS_DEFAULT_REGION=us-east-1

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy the configuration for your chosen SMS service
# 2. Paste it into your main .env file
# 3. Replace the x's with your actual credentials
# 4. Test the service using: php artisan tinker
